data.description: Welcome to your future home with 3 bedrooms, 1 bath, beautiful hardwood floors, ample parking in wide driveway, large backyard completely fenced in with a privacy fence, large shed, and a patio. Two fireplaces (living room and family room), high efficiency furnace and central air. Sub offers a deeded access lot on all sports Silver Lake. Windows have a lifetime warranty that can be transferred to the new owners. New fire pit and garden beds in the backyard.
